\c 24
\s Joashi anogadzira temberi; pashure anotsauka panzira dzaJehovha
\p
\v 1 Joashi akange ava wemakore manomwe pakutanga kwake kubata ushe; akabata ushe paJerusarema makore makumi mana; zita ramai vake rakange riri Zibhia weBheeri-Shebha.
\v 2 Joashi akaita zvakanaka pamberi paJehovha mazuva ese omupristi Jehoyadha.
\v 3 Jehoyadha akamutsvakira vakadzi vaviri; akabereka vanakomana navanasikana.
\p
\v 4 Zvino shure kwaizvozvi Joashi akarangarira kuvandudza imba yaJehovha.
\v 5 Akakokera vapristi naVaRevhi, akati kwavari: Budirai kumaguta aJudha, muunganidze kuVaIsraeri vese mari yokugadzirisa nayo imba yaMwari wenyu gore rimwe nerimwe; uye mubve machimbidzikira chinhu ichi! Asi VaRevhi havana kuchimbidzika.
\v 6 Zvino mambo akadana mukuru Jehoyadha, akati kwaari: Makaregereiko kuraira VaRevhi kundounganidza mutero waMozisi muranda waJehovha paJudha napaJerusarema napaungano yaIsraeri, zviiswe patende rechipupuriro?
\v 7 Nokuti vanakomana vaAtaria, mukadzi uya wakaipa, vakange vaputsa imba yaMwari; nezvinhu zvese zveimba yaJehovha, zvakange zvakatsaurirwa Mwari, vakazvipa vana Bhaari.
\v 8 Naizvozvo mambo akaraira, vakaveza bhokisi, vakariisa kunze kwesuwo reimba yaJehovha.
\v 9 Zvino vakatuma shoko pakati paJudha neJerusarema, kuti vanhu vavigire Jehovha mutero wakarairwa VaIsraeri murenje naMozisi muranda waMwari.
\v 10 Machinda ese navanhu vese vakafara, vakauya nazvo, vakazvikanda mubhokisi, kusvikira vapedza.
\v 11 Zvino nguva dzese kana bhokisi richiiswa paimba yamambo namaoko aVaRevhi, kana vakaona kuti mari zhinji yavamo, munyori wamambo nomutariri weupristi ukuru vakauya vakadurura zviri mubhokisi, vakaritora ndokuridzoserazve panzvimbo yaro. Vakaita kudaro zuva rimwe nerimwe, vakaunganidza mari zhinji.
\v 12 Zvino mambo naJehoyadha vakaipa vaibata mabasa paimba yaJehovha; vakaripira vavezi vamabwe namatanda, kuti vavandudze imba yaJehovha, navapfuri vamatare nendarira, kuti vagadzire imba yaJehovha.
\v 13 Naizvozvo vabati vakabata, basa rikapedzwa navo; vakamutsiridza imba yaMwari sezvayakange yakaita kare, vakaisimbisa.
\v 14 Zvino vakati vapedza, vakauya nemari yakasara kuna mambo naJehoyadha, vakaita nayo midziyo yeimba yaJehovha, iri midziyo yokubata nayo, nokubaira nayo, nezvirongo nemidziyo yegoridhe nesirivha. Vaibaira zvipiriso zvinopiswa mumba maJehovha mazuva ese aJehoyadha.
\p
\v 15 Asi Jehoyadha akazokwegura, akava namazuva mazhinji ndokufa; akange ava wemakore ane zana namakumi matatu pakufa kwake.
\v 16 Vakamuviga paguta raDhavhidhi pakati pamadzimambo; nokuti akange aitira Mwari neimba yake zvakanaka pakati paIsraeri.
\v 17 Zvino Jehoyadha akati afa, machinda aJudha akasvika, akanamata mambo. Ipapo mambo akavateerera.
\v 18 Vakasiya imba yaJehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo, vakashumira matanda avo okunamata nawo nezvifananidzo; Mwari akatsamwira Judha neJerusarema pamusoro pemhaka iyi.
\v 19 Kunyange zvakadaro akavatumira vaporofita kuzovadzoserazve kuna Jehovha; ivo vakavapupurira, asi vakaramba kunzwa.
\v 20 Ipapo Mweya waMwari wakauya pamusoro paZekariya, mwanakomana womupristi Jehoyadha, akamira pakakwirira pamberi pavanhu, akati kwavari: Zvanzi naMwari: Munodarikireiko mirairo yaJehovha, muchiramba kufara? Zvamasiya Jehovha, naiye wakakusiyayiwo.
\v 21 Ipapo vakarangana, vakamutaka namabwe paruvazhe rweimba yaJehovha, varairwa namambo.
\v 22 Nokudaro mambo Joashi haana kurangarira zvakanaka zvaakange aitirwa naJehoyadha baba vake, asi akauraya mwanakomana wake. Zvino wakati achifa, akati: Jehovha ngaatarire chinhu ichi, achitsive.
\p
\v 23 Zvino gore rakati ropera, hondo yavaSiriya ikasvika kuzorwa naye; vakasvika paJudha napaJerusarema vakaparadza machinda ese avanhu pakati pavanhu, vakatuma zvese zvavakapamba kuna mambo weDhamasiko.
\v 24 Nokuti hondo yavaSiriya yakauya neboka diki ravanhu; Jehovha akaisa pfumo guru-guru mumaoko avo, nokuti vakange vasiya Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo. Nokudaro vakaitira Joashi zvakange zvatongwa naMwari.
\v 25 Zvino vakati vabva kwaari (nokuti vakamusiya achirwara kwazvo), varanda vake vakarangana pamusoro pake nemhaka yeropa ravanakomana vomupristi Jehoyadha, vakamuuraira panhovo yake, akafa; vakamuviga muguta raDhavhidhi, asi havana kumuviga kumarinda amadzimambo.
\v 26 Vakarangana pamusoro pake ndivava: Zabhadhi mwanakomana waShimeati, mukadzi muAmoni, naJehozabhadhi mwanakomana waShimiriti mukadzi muMoabhu.
\p
\v 27 Zvino kana zviri zvavanakomana vake, namashoko makuru avaporofita akarehwa pamusoro pake, nokumutsiridzwa kweimba yaMwari, tarirai zvakanyorwa padudziro yebhuku yamadzimambo. Amazia mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
